Title: Quantum group treatment of substrate potential in Integer Quantum Hall Effect  
Author: Guang-Hong Chen 
Address: Salt Lake City, UT 84112  
Affiliation: Physics Department,The University of Utah,  
Abstract: By making use of quantum group techniques, we obtain an exactly solvable model, which describes the influence of general form of weak substrate potential on the lowest Landau level. Especially, for Gaussian type substrate potential, we give its Bethe ansatz solution by using the cyclic representation of quantum group U q (sl 2 ). 
